name: If

inputs.name: A > B
inputs.description: Return this value if A is greater than B.

inputs.name: A = B
inputs.description: Return this value if A is equal to B.

inputs.name: A < B
inputs.description: Return this value if A is less than B.

description: If expression. Return a given value depending on which one is greater between value A and B. For vectors, it's element-wise comparison.
